    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for icecast</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">The streaming server icecast was updated to fix a remote denial of service vulnerability.

A remote attacker could crash icecast and cause denial of service when URL Auth is configured and used with stream_auth without credentials (bnc#926402 CVE-2015-3026)
</Note>
